preference.name: CATIA_check_PX1_available
preference.preference_description: Behavior of Save processes based on usage of a PX1 license - Do not display a message when PX1 is not selected (NONE) - Display a message at the beginning of the process when PX1 is not selected. Provide a user prompt to continue or cancel the process. (WARNING) - Display an error message at the beginning of the process when PX1 is not selected and stop the process. (ERROR).
